casebody.data:
John Maybee v. Lester Miner, drain commissioner. G. T. Gridley for the motion.

Certiorari — Motion to quash.

Questions touching the merits on certiorari must be brought up on the hearing of the cause, and will not be considered on notice to quash.

Motion to quash eertiora/ri as improvidently issued.

Submitted and decided June 15.

Motion denied.
